This project is a research fork that ports AWS Firecracker's microVM VMM to
macOS on Apple Silicon, replacing KVM with Apple's Hypervisor.framework.

It contains and derives from the following Apache-2.0 works:

  - AWS Firecracker — https://github.com/firecracker-microvm/firecracker
    Copyright Amazon.com, Inc. or its affiliates. Licensed under Apache-2.0.

  - libkrun — https://github.com/containers/libkrun
    (itself Firecracker-derived) Licensed under Apache-2.0.
    The Hypervisor.framework backend (the `hvf` crate) is lifted from libkrun.

Portions of the source retain their original copyright and license notices.
